入坑可以找图一&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/14491e8171b0556958f13223a233e894.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/c06b37e0bb493a04ea7452cddaa5eefc.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/f5ea8d730d0f9f305877058d048fadb8.jpg&quot; &gt;</description><link>https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70999153</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70999153</guid><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 06:58:38 GMT</pubDate><author>Thisistheendof</author></item><item><title>用这手机加望远镜拍的月亮，好像还拍到了围绕月亮的陨石了，那种高度应该不是鸟，可惜这手机的酷安不支持实况图，不然更明显#DIY#</title><description>&lt;p&gt;用这手机加望远镜拍的月亮，好像还拍到了围绕月亮的陨石了，那种高度应该不是鸟，可惜这手机的酷安不支持实况图，不然更明显&lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/DIY?type=0&quot;&gt;#DIY#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/516c39ebe801a6376400750b3b3f6dde.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/1118f1a4777025e3f4cfb068257c3000.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/a73ac3c0c1088f4f0989fd2968b960da.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/9634d02643a8ec4f7a4752e68e467f46.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/57643d9d511d147f288f9b9399db1e91.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/e69f7cbc165d649aa25e224c337c8964.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/eaabd218f79281ff1b4b88272c253c30.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/dda97c80b9b535230f1d0ea9ac7a4402.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/b57baa6dfb393ae7587a65a322dd69aa.jpg&quot; &gt;</description><link>https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70987434</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70987434</guid><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 12:13:56 GMT</pubDate><author>麻咪麻咪呸</author></item><item><title>#diy充电宝# 推荐两块低价板子，自己DIY充电宝的话其实倍思的拆机主板挺不错的，标的是30w，但是是反向虚标，大约有33-35w，价格四五块钱，用的是两串三元锂电池...</title><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/diy%E5%85%85%E7%94%B5%E5%AE%9D?type=0&quot;&gt;#diy充电宝#&lt;/a&gt; 推荐两块低价板子，自己DIY充电宝的话其实倍思的拆机主板挺不错的，标的是30w，但是是反向虚标，大约有33-35w，价格四五块钱，用的是两串三元锂电池，不过因为是拆机主板，温度传感线可能会松动脱落导致不能用的话记得焊上去看图2，我买的就脱落了，当然也可以多花十块钱上他家65w主板图3，65w主板要4串电池，就需要上均衡了，两串的话内阻相差不大不上也没什么太大事情， &lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/DIY?type=0&quot;&gt;#DIY#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/405089a75adfd8e0c4232f77715f6241.jpeg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/b5b539e0eb7b5d718c858091e808c280.jpeg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/a2f6c3e929285656c658e46de3f0c17d.jpeg&quot; &gt;</description><link>https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70973306</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70973306</guid><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 16:41:44 GMT</pubDate><author>图图没耳朵</author></item><item><title>#DIY# 除去magsafe 50块搞定，直接干出水来🐶，搭配安克1a1c 33w充电头，iPhone air 全程冰冰凉，40%到80%40分钟没办法air充电功率上不去😭后面换港版25w ma...</title><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/DIY?type=0&quot;&gt;#DIY#&lt;/a&gt;  除去magsafe 50块搞定，直接干出水来🐶，搭配安克1a1c  33w充电头，iPhone air 全程冰冰凉，40%到80%40分钟没办法air充电功率上不去😭后面换港版25w  magsafe不知道会不会好一些。&lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/%E5%85%85%E7%94%B5%E5%A4%B4%E5%85%B4%E8%B6%A3%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%84?type=0&quot;&gt;#充电头兴趣小组#&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/MagSafe%E7%A3%81%E5%90%B8%E6%97%A0%E7%BA%BF%E5%85%85%E7%94%B5%E5%99%A8?type=0&quot;&gt;#MagSafe磁吸无线充电器#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/377d6467692b3c8cc73ae97670a7f6b1.jpeg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/0f264de4c095f0d6707c5db374c4a1f2.jpeg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/b490a9c639f5ea6a3e40a3c922f40b93.jpeg&quot; &gt;</description><link>https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70965038</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70965038</guid><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 09:43:53 GMT</pubDate><author>三9感冒灵</author></item><item><title>【手提箱diy机箱。】这显卡，还需要买啥配件，一下子猝到了。[流泪]</title><description>&lt;p&gt;【手提箱diy机箱。】这显卡，还需要买啥配件，一下子猝到了。[流泪]&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/f3f3f38b854e19ff69a7768d579b527f.jpg&quot; &gt;</description><link>https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70964523</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70964523</guid><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 09:13:08 GMT</pubDate><author>I热心网友I</author></item></channel></rss>